<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="avoid-vt">avoid <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ə'vɔɪd/    美 /ə'vɔɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>避免；防止</strong></h4>
<p>to prevent sth bad from happening：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Road safety is taught to young children to avoid road accident. 
儿童需要学习道路安全知识，以避免交通事故。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>avoid doing sth: </li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To avoid missing the last train, please check the last train times posted in stations.
为了避免错过末班列车，请查阅车站张贴的末班列车时刻表。</p><footer>2014 全国</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>回避；避开</strong></h4>
<p>to stay away from sb or sth, or to deliberately not do sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Generally we dislike arguments, and we avoid topics which lead to disagreement. 
我们通常不喜欢争吵，会回避引起争执的话题。</p><footer>外研⑥ – 1</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>avoid doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Neighbors should do all they can to avoid disturbing other people. 
邻居应尽量避免打扰他人。</p><footer>2014 湖南</footer></div>

<p>注: avoid不接不定式作宾语。  </p>
<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I quickly lower myself, ducking my head to avoid<strong><em>_</em></strong>__(look) directly into his eyes.   （2018 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. looking  </p></div>